    "Russian cuisine in Erfurt"

    If you are in Erfurt and you want to try Russian food "Uralskie pelmeni" is the place for you. "Uralskie pelmeni" is the name of a small Russian snack bar/ restaurant at Johannesstraße 35. It is a type of self- serve eatery. Everything at this...place is guaranteed fresh and made according to traditional Russian recipes. The options are not vast, but Russian dumplings pelmeni and vareniki are always available and of course the Russian "kvass" to drink. The staff are very friendly and service is great. Eating in the "Uralskie pelmeni" won't create a hole in your pocket. I really recommend this place. My husband and I were very satisfied by our visit.More

    Date of visit: September 2016
